        <section id="overview" class="content-section active">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Ecological Site Inspection Overview</h2>
            
            <div class="learning-objectives">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Learning Objectives</h3>
                <p>By the end of this module, you will be able to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Understand the purpose and importance of ecological site inspections</li>
                    <li>Identify key components of a comprehensive site inspection</li>
                    <li>Recognize Tasmania's unique ecological features and conservation values</li>
                    <li>Apply appropriate assessment techniques for different ecosystem types</li>
