                    <ul>
                        <li>Identification and mapping of giant trees</li>
                        <li>Legal protection through forest practices regulations</li>
                        <li>Community advocacy and awareness campaigns</li>
                        <li>Reservation of key areas containing giant trees</li>
                        <li>Research into the ecological role of these trees</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4>Outcomes</h4>
                    <p>Many significant giant trees now have formal protection, though debates continue about the balance between conservation and resource use. Public awareness of these remarkable trees has increased significantly.</p>
