                    <h4>Response</h4>
                    <p>Management approaches include:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Biosecurity measures to prevent new introductions</li>
                        <li>Monitoring programs to detect new incursions early</li>
                        <li>Research into control methods for established pests</li>
                        <li>Community reporting programs</li>
                        <li>Development of a marine pest management strategy</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4>Outcomes</h4>
